          About 40% of our Fort Lauderdale clients have pets. Dog hair removal is one of our most requested add-on services, especially from owners who take their dogs to the beach or dog parks like Bark Park or Snyder Park dog area.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-4">How Much Does Pet Hair Removal Cost in Fort Lauderdale?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          <strong>Pet hair removal in Fort Lauderdale costs $50 to $100 depending on how much hair we're dealing with.</strong>
        </p>
