          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-1">AC contamination</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Loose hair gets pulled into vents and circulates through your cabin.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#0f2a4a] mb-1">Resale impact</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Pet hair is one of the first things buyers notice when looking at a used car.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Signs you need professional pet hair removal:</p>
